name: Push Up
benefit: Pushups are a type of strength building exercise.

name: Pull Up
benefit: The pullup is one of the most effective exercises for strengthening the back muscles.

name: Treadmill
benefit: A treadmill is a device generally used for walking, running, or climbing.

name: Barbell
benefit: Barbell is used for free weight training and competitive sports, such as powerlifting, Olympic weight lifting, and CrossFit.

name: Weight Plate
benefit: Weight Plate is used in combination with barbells or dumbbells to produce a bar with a desired total weight for the purpose of physical exercise.

name: Exercise Roller
benefit: Exercise Roller can help relieve muscle tightness, soreness, and inflammation, and increase your joint range of motion.
